Useful Websites for Experimental Mathematics
Here is a list of links to numerous useful websites of general interest to mathematicians in general, and to experimental mathematicians in particular.
This list is basically the same as given in Section 1.8 of Vol. 1.
We will attempt to keep these links up-to-date in case any of them change with the passage of time.
